form:listbox.form:list-source: select Status,Status from Status order by Status ASC
select distinct year(Erstellungsdatum),year(Erstellungsdatum) as Jahr from Rechnungen1 order by Jahr DESC

select distinct t1.Monat,t1.MonatID FROM (Monate as t1 INNER JOIN Rechnungen1 as t2 ON t1.MonatID = Month(t2.Erstellungsdatum)) INNER JOIN Steuerung as t3 ON t3.ClientID=30 where (((YEAR(t2.Erstellungsdatum)=t3.Jahr and LENGTH(t3.Jahr) > 0) or (YEAR(t2.Erstellungsdatum) like '%' and (LENGTH(t3.Jahr) IS NULL OR LENGTH(t3.Jahr)=0))) or t1.MonatID=t3.Monat) order by t1.MonatID ASC

select distinct t1.Status,t1.Status as Stat from Rechnungen1 as t1 INNER JOIN Steuerung as t2 ON t2.ClientID=30 where (((YEAR(t1.Erstellungsdatum)=t2.Jahr and LENGTH(t2.Jahr) > 0) or (YEAR(t1.Erstellungsdatum) like '%' and (LENGTH(t2.Jahr) IS NULL OR LENGTH(t2.Jahr)=0))) and ((MONTH(t1.Erstellungsdatum)=t2.Monat and LENGTH(t2.Monat) > 0) or (MONTH(t1.Erstellungsdatum) like '%' and (LENGTH(t2.Monat) IS NULL OR LENGTH(t2.Monat)=0))) or t1.Status=t2.Status)

select distinct concat(t3.Name1,' --> ',t1.Document_Name) as Name,t1.DocumentID from (Rechnungen1 as t1 INNER JOIN Kunden as t3 ON t3.KontaktID=t1.KontaktID) INNER JOIN Steuerung as t2 ON t2.ClientID=30 where ((((YEAR(t1.Erstellungsdatum)=t2.Jahr and LENGTH(t2.Jahr) > 0) or (YEAR(t1.Erstellungsdatum) like '%' and (LENGTH(t2.Jahr) IS NULL OR LENGTH(t2.Jahr)=0))) and ((MONTH(t1.Erstellungsdatum)=t2.Monat and LENGTH(t2.Monat) > 0) or (MONTH(t1.Erstellungsdatum) like '%' and (LENGTH(t2.Monat) IS NULL OR LENGTH(t2.Monat)=0))) and ((t1.Status=t2.Status and LENGTH(t2.Status) > 0) or (t1.Status like '%' and (LENGTH(t2.Status) IS NULL OR LENGTH(t2.Status)=0))) and ((t1.Document_Name like concat('%',t2.Suchstring,'%') and LENGTH(t2.Suchstring) > 0) or (t1.Document_Name like '%' and (LENGTH(t2.Suchstring) IS NULL OR LENGTH(t2.Suchstring)=0))) and ((t1.KontaktID=t2.KundenID and LENGTH(t2.KundenID) > 0) or (t1.KontaktID like '%' and (LENGTH(t2.KundenID) IS NULL OR LENGTH(t2.KundenID)=0)))) or t1.DocumentID=t2.DocumentID) order by t1.DocumentID DESC

form:fixed-text.form:label: Summe der offenen Rechnungen des Kunden

form:listbox.form:list-source: select distinct year(t1.Erstellungsdatum),year(t1.Erstellungsdatum) as Jahr from Rechnungen1 as t1 order by Jahr DESC

select distinct concat(t3.Name1,' ',t3.Vorname,' ',t3.Name2,' --> ',t3.Ort) as Name,t1.KontaktID from (Rechnungen1 as t1 INNER JOIN Kunden as t3 ON t3.KontaktID=t1.KontaktID) INNER JOIN Steuerung as t2 ON t2.ClientID=30 where (((YEAR(t1.Erstellungsdatum)=t2.Jahr and LENGTH(t2.Jahr) > 0) or (YEAR(t1.Erstellungsdatum) like '%' and (LENGTH(t2.Jahr) IS NULL OR LENGTH(t2.Jahr)=0))) and ((MONTH(t1.Erstellungsdatum)=t2.Monat and LENGTH(t2.Monat) > 0) or (MONTH(t1.Erstellungsdatum) like '%' and (LENGTH(t2.Monat) IS NULL OR LENGTH(t2.Monat)=0))) and ((t1.Status=t2.Status and LENGTH(t2.Status) > 0) or (t1.Status like '%' and (LENGTH(t2.Status) IS NULL OR LENGTH(t2.Status)=0))) or t1.KontaktID=t2.KundenID) order by t3.Name1 ASC
